# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# __rmod__ dict-presence — operator.contains(Cls.__dict__, '__rmod__')
#
# All 8 multiprocessing classes return false for __rmod__.
# Process/Pool/AsyncResult/MapResult/SyncManager: process-management types;
#   reflected modulo is not defined.
# managers.BaseListProxy: proxies list — list does NOT define __rmod__.
#   list has no format-string or modulo semantics from either side.
# managers._BaseDictProxy: proxies dict — dict defines no __rmod__.
# managers._BaseSetProxy: proxies set — set defines no modulo operator from
#   either side; sets are not str-like types and do not support % formatting.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

